freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I had four ocular migraines of short duration. Only the last one developed into a full-blown headache. In the past I have had one or two of these per year, but never four clustered in one week.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I should have reported this yesterday for the day before. On the day I had the headache I did not sleep that night. Went to bed 11PM fell asleep 6:30AM until 8:00AM. Could not go back to sleep. Went to bed last 9:00PM - 7:30AM and slept well
Napping yesterday afternoon messed up my sleep rhythm. Didnt fall asleep until 3AM.
